article_title: Obamacare 101: What you need to get insured
article_text:

article_metadata.description: A very important date is quickly approaching: Obamacare open enrollment begins November 15th.  Health insurance is required by law now, so if you're unemployed or your employer doesn't provide it, it's time to figure out how you're going to get your insurance for 2015.
article_metadata.author: HLN Staff
